[14/01/2019 11:00:59] <font color="#ffffff">-Sí.</font>
[14/01/2019 11:00:59] <font color="#ffffff">-Un salto descomunal.</font>
[14/01/2019 11:01:02] <font color="#ffffff">-Hola, niñas,</font>
