[14/01/2019 22:47:32] <font color="#ffffff">(Ruido)</font>
[14/01/2019 22:47:34] <font color="#00ffff">(OFF) "Le pesaba".</font>
[14/01/2019 22:47:35] <font color="#00ffff">"Medía su altura,</font>
[14/01/2019 22:47:38] <font color="#00ffff">y el cuello".</font>
[14/01/2019 22:47:45] <font color="#00ff00">"¿Con qué objetivo</font>
