[14/01/2019 22:48:03] <font color="#00ff00">Y si... calculaba mal</font>
[14/01/2019 22:48:03] <font color="#00ff00">la caída de Eben,</font>
[14/01/2019 22:48:06] <font color="#00ff00">¿podría no haber muerto</font>
[14/01/2019 22:48:06] <font color="#00ff00">al instante</font>
[14/01/2019 22:48:12] <font color="#00ff00">y haber sufrido?</font>
[14/01/2019 22:48:15] <font color="#00ffff">Sí.</font>
[14/01/2019 22:48:22] <font color="#00ff00">Es una gran responsabilidad,</font>
[14/01/2019 22:48:22] <font color="#00ff00">¿verdad?</font>
[14/01/2019 22:48:26] <font color="#00ff00">¿Cuánto tiempo tarda un hombre</font>
