[14/01/2019 22:50:12] <font color="#00ffff">¡Nada!</font>
[14/01/2019 22:50:15] <font color="#00ffff">No sentí nada.</font>
[14/01/2019 22:50:18] <font color="#00ffff">No pensé nada. Solo cansancio.</font>
