[14/01/2019 23:41:25] <font color="#ffff00">y Francisco Franco</font>
[14/01/2019 23:41:30] <font color="#ffff00">en calidad de director</font>
[14/01/2019 23:41:30] <font color="#ffff00">de la Academia General Militar.</font>
